<s> Stop right there -- that's not clear at all.  </s>
<s> There is no consensus that anything marked up with the acronym tag is meant to be pronounced in any given manner in any given language.  </s>
<s> Yes, and inconclusively so.  </s>
<s> There is no link between acronym and any given pronunciation of the content of the element.  </s>
<s> There is currently no way to mark up a specific pronunciation for any text in (X)HTML.  </s>
<s> Your question can be applied equally to non-acronym text as well: Do I spell 'wright' the write way when I right it with my rite hand?  </s>
